HEADWORD: Ha-ha
<hw>Ha-ha"</hw> <pr>(h⟦aum⟧*h⟦aum⟧")</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Haw-haw</er>.]</ety> <def>A sunk fence; a fence, wall, or ditch, not
visible till one is close upon it.</def> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>haw-haw</asp>.]</altsp>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

